#

Truffle Mushroom Risotto with Grilled Asparagus

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

DairyMushrooms

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A luxurious blend of creamy risotto infused with truffle oil and earthy mushrooms, paired with perfectly grilled asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Chicken or vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • Fresh mushrooms (cremini or shiitake): 2 cups, sliced
  • Onion: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
